_sText:
This is a remake of my older map that was for Counter-Strike 1.0 also works in 1.6. I remade it from scratch for Counter-strike: Source.

This map has 32 spawns but it was really designed for 24 players or less.

============================================================

New nav file as of 1/20/08 re-download the zip for greatly improved bots and hostages.

New edited nav file by Chizbone.

Read the readme inside the zip for more info.
